<br>
This could also potentially be used a recruiting tool (I'm not as sure about this part).  We could let newbies into the Alt guild, and see how they handle guild chat and such before inviting them into the &quot;real&quot; guild.  That way, KoN would be kind of an honor guild for the few, the proud, and those with maturity that exceeds the average sixth grader's.   A guild that was less picky and that consisted mainly of low level players would likely grow much faster then KoN, and might even turn up decent players we would not have found otherwise. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub27.ezboard.com/fknightsofnorrath91133frm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=33.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub27.ezboard.com/fknightsofnorrath91133frm2.showNextMessage?topicID=33.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub27.ezboard.com/fknightsofnorrath91133frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=33.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub27.ezboard.com/fknightsofnorrath91133frm2.emailToFriend?topicID=33.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub27.ezboard.com/fknightsofnorrath91133frm2.threadControl?topicID=33.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub27.ezboard.com/fknightsofnorrath91133frm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=33.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub27.ezbo